    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-11T19:30:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-10T19:00:00-05:00" n="1147"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1147">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 138.4/22</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_HMT1">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Secretary of State</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content"
                        calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1914-08-11T19:30:00-05:00"
                        notBefore="1914-08-11T00:00:00+00:00">
                        <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                    </date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received August 11, 1914, 7:30 p.m.</hi>] </dateline>
                <p rend="center">[Telegram]</p>
                <p>Earnestly request immediate instructions concerning granting individuals holding
                    first papers certificate of identity to secure temporary <hi rend="italic"
                        >permis de sejour</hi> pending opportunity to return to United States.</p>
                <closer>[File copy not signed]</closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_HMT1" type="to">
                            <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                        </persName>)</head>
                    <note rend="inline" rendition="#center">[Telegram]</note>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                            </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-12">
                                <hi rend="italic">August 12, 1914</hi>
                            </date>.</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>Certificates of identity may be issued to persons holding first papers,
                        provided seven years have not elapsed and residence of a permanent nature
                        has not been acquired abroad since they were obtained. Inform Consulate
                        General.</p>
                    <p rend="right">
                        <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </p>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
